tagProvider = value['tagProvider']
	derivedFromUDTFolder = value['derivedFromUDTFolder']
	
	#Get ParentTagProviderFolderPath Parameter from Model Item Parameters
	fromFolder = '['+tagProvider+']_types_/'+derivedFromUDTFolder+"/Model/Model Item"
	fromTags = system.tag.getConfiguration(basePath=fromFolder, recursive=False)
	parentTagProviderFolderPath = modelItemParameters = fromTags[0]['parameters']['ParentTagProviderFolderPath'].value
	
	fromFolder = '['+tagProvider+']_types_/'+derivedFromUDTFolder+"/Control Modules/AI"
	fromTags = system.tag.getConfiguration(basePath=fromFolder, recursive=False)
	opcServerName = modelItemParameters = fromTags[0]['parameters']['OPCServerName'].value
	opcPath = modelItemParameters = fromTags[0]['parameters']['OPCPath'].value
	historyStorageProvider = modelItemParameters = fromTags[0]['parameters']['HistoryStorageProvider'].value
	historyModelPathPrefix = modelItemParameters = fromTags[0]['parameters']['HistoryModelPathPrefix'].value
	
	parameters = {
	  "ParentTagProviderFolderPath": parentTagProviderFolderPath,
	  "OPCServerName": opcServerName,
	  "OPCPath": opcPath,
	  "HistoryStorageProvider": historyStorageProvider,
	  "HistoryModelPathPrefix": historyModelPathPrefix
	}
	return parameters

tags=system.tag.browse(filter={"tagType":"Provider"}).results
	arrTagProviders=[]
	for result in tags:
		provider=str(result['fullPath'])
		if provider != "[System]":
			arrTagProviders.append(provider)
	return arrTagProviders

tagProvider = value['tagProvider']
	derivedFromUDTFolder = value['derivedFromUDTFolder']
	
	fromFolder = '['+tagProvider+']_types_/'+derivedFromUDTFolder
	fromTags = system.tag.getConfiguration(basePath=fromFolder, recursive=True)
	
	return fromTags[0]

tagProvider = value['tagProvider']
	fromUDT = value['fromUDT']
	toUDTFolder = value['toUDTFolder']
	derivedFromUDTFolder = value['derivedFromUDTFolder'] 
	parametersConfig = value['parameters'] 
	j='/'
	#return j.join(newTypeId)
	self.custom.faultTags = None
	toFolder = '['+tagProvider+']_types_'
	#return 
	def getFolder(fromFolder,path=''):
		folderName = fromFolder['name']
		fullPath = folderName
		if len(path)>0:
			fullPath = path + '/' + folderName
	 	newFolder = {"name": folderName,"tagType" : 'Folder'}
	 	
	 	#get udts
	 	tags = []
	 	for tag in fromFolder['tags']:
	 		name = tag['name']
	 		
	 		
	 		tagType = tag['tagType']
	 		if tagType == 'Folder':
	 			newtag = getFolder(tag,fullPath)
	 		elif tagType == 'UdtType':
	 			params = None
	 			if 'parameters' in tag:
	 				params = tag['parameters']
	 			if 'typeId' not in tag:
	 				self.custom.faultTags = tag 
	 				break
	 			typeId = fullPath+'/'+name
	 			newtag = {"name": name,"tagType" : tagType,'typeId':typeId}
	 			if 'parameters' in tag:
	 				params = tag['parameters']
	 				newParams = {}
	 				for parKey in params:
	 					
	 					if parKey in parametersConfig:
	 						newParams[parKey] = parametersConfig[parKey]
	 				
	 				newtag['parameters'] = newParams
	 		tags.append(newtag)
	 	newFolder['tags'] = tags
	 	return newFolder

	baseFoler = getFolder(fromUDT,'')
	baseFoler['name'] = toUDTFolder
	return baseFoler

config.script:
tagProvider = self.view.custom.tagProvider
	toUDT = self.view.custom.toUDT
	
	toFolder = '['+tagProvider+']_types_/'
	collisionPolicy = "o" #Overwrite, "a" #abort
	self.view.custom.response = "Configuring...."
	qualityCodes = system.tag.configure(basePath=toFolder, tags=toUDT,collisionPolicy = collisionPolicy)
	self.view.custom.response = "Configured:" + str(qualityCodes[0])
